title: Steele eager to get started, and it showed at Silverado
text:
> Sports Steele eager to get started, and it showed at Silverado Rory McIlroy, of Northern Ireland, chips the ball onto the ninth green of the Silverado Resort North Course during the first round of the Frys.com PGA Tour golf tournament Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Napa, Calif. (AP Photo/Eric Risberg)
